# Purpose: Docker build context exclusion patterns for optimized image builds and security
# Scope: All Docker build operations for thai-lint project
# Overview: Defines patterns for files and directories to exclude from Docker build context,
#     reducing image size, improving build performance, and preventing sensitive data from
#     being copied into Docker images. Excludes version control files, Python cache, test
#     files, documentation, CI/CD configs, and development tools that are not needed in
#     production containers.
# Dependencies: Docker build process
# Exports: Build context exclusion patterns for .dockerignore
# Environment: All Docker build contexts (development and production)
# Related: Dockerfile, docker-compose.yml
# Implementation: Standard .dockerignore patterns following Docker best practices

